    "highlights": "<p>Recent snow and wind have produced dangerous avalanche conditions at higher elevations.</p>",
    "confidence": {
      "rating": {
        "value": "moderate",
        "display": "Moderate"
      },
      "statements": [
        "Uncertainty is due to how quickly the snowpack will recover and gain strength."
      ]
    },
    "summaries": [
      {
        "type": {
          "value": "avalanche-summary",
          "display": "Avalanche Summary"
        },
        "content": " <p>Explosive control work on Thursday morning produced reactive slabs in wind-loaded, northerly terrain, up to size 1.5.</p><p>On Wednesday, numerous explosive and skier-triggered storm slab avalanches were reported across a variety of aspects and elevations, up to size 2.</p>"
      },
      {
        "type": {
          "value": "snowpack-summary",
          "display": "Snowpack Summary"
        },
        "content": " <p>Approximately 30 to 60 cm of recent storm snow has accumulated, accompanied by strong to extreme southerly alpine winds.</p><p>Below the recent snow, a melt-freeze crust is present at elevations of 2200 m and below. The depth of this layer is highly variable due to extensive recent wind transport.</p><p>A crust with associated facets, formed in mid-November, is buried an estimated 80 to 150 cm deep. This layer remains a concern in alpine terrain where it has not been capped by a strong overlying crust.</p>"
      },
      {
        "type": {
          "value": "weather-summary",
          "display": "Weather Summary"
        },
        "content": " <p><strong>Thursday Night</strong><br>Mostly cloudy.  5 to 10 cm of snow. 30 km/h southwest ridgetop wind. Treeline temperature -5 째C. <br><br><strong>Friday</strong><br>Mostly cloudy.  5 to 10 cm of snow. 20 km/h southwest ridgetop wind. Treeline temperature -7 째C. </p><p><br><strong>Saturday</strong><br>Mostly cloudy. 20 to 30 cm of snow. 30 km/h southwest ridgetop wind. Treeline temperature -6 째C. <br><br><strong>Sunday</strong><br>Mostly cloudy. 15 to 20 cm of snow. 20 km/h south ridgetop wind. Treeline temperature -4 째C. </p> <p>More details can be found in the <a href =\"https://www.avalanche.ca/weather/forecast\">Mountain Weather Forecast</a>.</p>"
      }
